01:39.184 --> 01:41.564
- Dory. Dory. Dory, honey.
- Dory. Kelpcake.

01:41.686 --> 01:43.396
Undertow, sweetie.

01:44.063 --> 01:47.113
Remember, honey, we have to
stay away from the undertow.

01:47.275 --> 01:49.435
Okay, sweetheart,
what about that rhyme we learned?

01:49.611 --> 01:52.451
# We see the undertow and we say...

01:52.530 --> 01:53.490
